            <title>[CAMEL-19783] camel-salesforce - grpc will not resubscribe on connection failure if no messages have been received</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-19783</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Relevant log:&lt;/p&gt;

